cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the use of mobile phone data and machine learning techniques to build data-driven intelligent mobile applications, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC), large-scale data analysis (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), social and information networks (cs.SI), and cybersecurity (cs.CY) to ensure the privacy and security of the collected data.
